{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"geometryGroup"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By default OpenSwiftUI views push position and size changes down","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"through the view hierarchy, so that only views that draw","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"something (known as leaf views) apply the current animation to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"their frame rectangle. However in some cases this coalescing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"behavior can give undesirable results; inserting a geometry","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"group can correct that. A group acts as a barrier between the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"parent view and its subviews, forcing the position and size","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values to be resolved and animated by the parent, before being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"passed down to each subview.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example below shows one use of this function: ensuring that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the member views of each row in the stack apply (and animate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as) a single geometric transform from their ancestor view,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"rather than letting the effects of the ancestor views be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"applied separately to each leaf view. If the members of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ItemView"},{"type":"text","text":" may be added and removed at different times the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group ensures that they stay locked together as animations are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"applied."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["VStack {","    ForEach(items) { item in","        ItemView(item: item)","            .geometryGroup()","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns: a new view whose geometry is isolated from that of its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parent view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"geometryGroup","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"}],"symbolKind":"method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Render\/RendererEffect\/RendererEffect.swift#L294","fileName":"RendererEffect.swift"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE13geometryGroupQryF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore4PathV","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"10.15","name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"1.0","name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"6.0","name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false}],"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","title":"geometryGroup()","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Path\/geometryGroup()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Path"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/path\/geometrygroup()"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Isolates the geometry (e.g. position and size) of the view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from its parent view."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/View":{"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"View","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"View","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that represents part of your app’s user interface and provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modifiers that you use to configure views."}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/view","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","role":"symbol"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Path/geometryGroup()":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Path\/geometryGroup()","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/path\/geometrygroup()","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Isolates the geometry (e.g. position and size) of the view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from its parent view."}],"title":"geometryGroup()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"geometryGroup","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui","type":"topic","title":"OpenSwiftUI","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declare the user interface and behavior for your app on every platform."}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Path":{"abstract":[{"text":"The outline of a 2D shape.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Path","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Path","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Path","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Path","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/path"}}}